Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to this exceptional live/work residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Step inside this sprawling 3,500 sq. ft. bungalow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Feel the warmth of elevated living throughout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Five spacious bedrooms invite relaxation and comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Each bedroom offers unique charm and flexibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Four well-appointed bathrooms ensure convenience for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Picture gatherings in the expansive open living area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The chef&apos;s kitchen is a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine cooking on gorgeous marble countertops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Natural light cascades through every corner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The heated workshop is a creative haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Perfect for projects or hobbies you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Two separate driveways offer incredible accessibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Direct access to the rear yard enhances privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Just a minute from Highway 401’s convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Future industrial zoning potential adds remarkable value.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This home is truly a rare find.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine the possibilities this space holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for joining this special tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}We hope you feel at home here.
